---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="MarsSoft EdgeSync - Uç Noktalar İçin MLOps Ajanı">
  <main class="bg-neutral-900 text-gray-300">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative py-32 px-4 overflow-hidden text-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
          Uç Noktalar İçin <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-orange-500">MLOps Ajanı</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          AWS S3 tabanlı modellerinizi Raspberry Pi, Jetson Nano veya On-Premise sunucularınıza güvenle dağıtın. Golang gücüyle sıfır bağımlılık.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center space-x-4 mb-8">
          <span class="bg-red-900/40 text-orange-400 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Written in Go</span>
          <span class="bg-red-900/40 text-orange-400 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Zero Runtime Deps</span>
          <span class="bg-red-900/40 text-orange-400 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">&lt; 50MB RAM</span>
        </div>
        <a href="#docs" class="px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-700 to-orange-600 text-white rounded-xl font-bold shadow-lg shadow-red-700/30 hover:scale-105 transition transform">
          Dokümantasyonu Oku
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[500px] bg-red-800 rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why EdgeSync? Grid -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-neutral-900 border-y border-red-900/50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-white mb-12">Neden EdgeSync?</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-red-900/50">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4"></div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Tekil Binary & Hafiflik</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Python veya Node.js bağımlılığı yok. Tek bir çalıştırılabilir dosya. %1 CPU ve 50MB RAM altında çalışan ultra-verimli mimari.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-red-900/50">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4"></div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Atomik Dağıtım</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Symlink (Sembolik Bağ) değişimi ile milisaniyeler içinde versiyon geçişi. Kesinti yok, servis durdurma yok.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-red-900/50">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4"></div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Otomatik Rollback</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Deploy scriptiniz (exit code != 0) hata verirse, ajan anında bir önceki stabil versiyona geri döner.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works Section -->
    <section id="docs" class="py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-12">Çalışma Prensibi: Polling & Execution</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-8 text-white">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-500">1.</span>
            <p>S3 Watch: Ajan, S3 Bucket'ındaki ETag değişikliklerini izler.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-red-500 text-2xl font-mono">&gt;</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-500">2.</span>
            <p>Verify: Yeni modeli indirir ve bütünlüğünü doğrular (Checksum).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-red-500 text-2xl font-mono">&gt;</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-500">3.</span>
            <p>Test: `deploy.sh --test` komutunu çalıştırır.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-red-500 text-2xl font-mono">&gt;</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-500">4.</span>
            <p>Swap: Başarılıysa Symlink'i günceller.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8 text-gray-400 italic">Not: IAM Rolleri ile tam entegrasyon. Access Key yönetimine son.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Installation Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-neutral-900 border-y border-red-900/50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">60 Saniyede Kurulum</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Linux (AMD64/ARM64) sisteminize tek komutla kurun.</p>
            <div class="bg-black rounded-lg p-4 text-left font-mono text-sm text-green-400 border border-red-900/50">
                <span class="text-gray-500">$</span> curl -sfL https://marssoft.com/install.sh | sh
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Specs Table Section -->
    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-white mb-12">Teknik Özellikler</h2>
            <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 border border-red-900/50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-4">
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <dt class="font-semibold text-white">Desteklenen İşletim Sistemleri:</dt>
                        <dd class="text-gray-400">Linux (Ubuntu, Debian, Alpine)</dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <dt class="font-semibold text-white">Mimariler:</dt>
                        <dd class="text-gray-400">x86_64, ARM64 (Raspberry Pi/Jetson Support)</dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <dt class="font-semibold text-white">Model Kaynağı:</dt>
                        <dd class="text-gray-400">AWS S3</dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <dt class="font-semibold text-white">Yapılandırma:</dt>
                        <dd class="text-gray-400">JSON based (/etc/edgesync/config.json)</dd>
                    </div>
                </dl>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>